Caption.String: Balance of System Model Detailed Results
The LandBOSSE model may take a few moments to load and run.

The first time you enable the NREL Land-Based Balance of System (LandBOSSE) cost model, SAM installs the model, which may take a few minutes. Once it is installed, enable the model to calculate BOS costs based on the model inputs. See Help for details and references.
Calculate BOS costs based on the inputs you entered. See below for results.
Replace SAM balance of system cost input with estimate from BOS cost model.
